<br>
I wish alcoholics would be potheads instead, then some kids out there wouldn't be beat by a drunken father.  There would be far less accidents... all the potheads would be driving 10 mph under the speed limit.<br>
<br>
I think the most important thing is that if you are drinking alcohol and saying pot is bad, then you had problems... alcohol is a poison that the liver fucking hates to have to battle all the time.  THC is a happy little chemical that spreads love and happiness. :-p<br>
